@@TJvColorButton.Color
Summary
  Specifies the currently selected color in the button.
Description
  Use Color to specify the color to display on the button. \Read Color to determine what color is
  currently selected. You can't change the color of the actual button as this is determined by the
  clBtnFace color constant.

